    public static final class EnumSerializer.EnumSerializerConfigSnapshot<T extends java.lang.Enum<T>>
extends GenericTypeSerializerConfigSnapshot<T>
    Configuration snapshot of a serializer for enumerations. Configuration contains the enum class, and an array of the enum's constants that existed when the configuration snapshot was taken.

      • getCompatibleVersions

        public int[] getCompatibleVersions()
        从类复制的说明: VersionedIOReadableWritable
        Returns the compatible version values.

        By default, the base implementation recognizes only the current version (identified by Versioned.getVersion()) as compatible. This method can be used as a hook and may be overridden to identify more compatible versions.

        覆盖:
